# Allow GitHub CLI Read Operations
# These commands are safe to run without confirmation.

Auto-allow these read-only gh commands:

- `gh pr view` — view pull request details
- `gh pr list` — list pull requests
- `gh pr diff` — view pull request diff
- `gh pr checks` — view PR check status
- `gh issue view` — view issue details
- `gh issue list` — list issues
- `gh repo view` — view repository info
- `gh api` (GET requests) — read GitHub API data
